Comment: 1,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and any help I could get, even yours, would be helpful.
Comment: 1,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Comment: 1,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Comment: 1,0:02:15.09,0:02:18.65,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama, do you plan\Nto give chocolate to anyone?
Comment: 1,0:04:15.83,0:04:16.93,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Where's Yamaji-san?
Comment: 1,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.56,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Yamaji-san!
Comment: 1,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.62,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Teru-chan.
Comment: 1,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.09,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Teru-chan!
Comment: 1,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.90,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Teru-chan, thanks for always taking care of me!
Comment: 1,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.38,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,It's because of Youko-sama's story.
Comment: 1,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.97,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Good for you, Hayama-chan.
Comment: 1,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.37,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Hayama-san's a model pet owner?
Comment: 1,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.83,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Then, Nishiyama-san, this\Nhappen to you too, I wonder?
Comment: 1,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.18,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Eru-chan giving you\Na repayment gift I mean.
Comment: 1,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.18,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Beelzebub-samaaaaa!
Comment: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.93,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,And it's Nishikawa Youko-sama to you.
Comment: 1,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.76,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Add the "-sama" you glutton!
Comment: 1,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.31,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama is being considerate!
Comment: 1,0:10:49.48,0:10:56.81,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,You know, uh, Nishi... hara... kawa... tani-san?
Comment: 1,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.03,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,It's Nishikawa-san.
Comment: 1,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.93,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Right, right, Nishikawa-san!
Comment: 1,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.03,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Why did you say weird things to Nishikawa-san?!
Comment: 1,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.83,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,You probably made\NNishikawa-san feel awkward!
Comment: 1,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.73,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Nishikawa-san and I aren't that close yet.
Comment: 1,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.89,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,When I give Yuu-kun the chocolates,\NI want it to be memorable.
Comment: 1,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.48,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,So that's what Usuda-sama is planning?
Comment: 1,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.73,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,—or rather Youko-sama's paw,\Nwould be helpful.
Comment: 1,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.18,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama wants to make\Nhandmade chocolate{ from scratch}?
Comment: 1,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.98,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,I was asking Nishiyama-san to\Ngive me a hand at the shop.
Comment: 1,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.21,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,By all means{I would love if you could help out}, Hayama-san too.
Comment: 1,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.01,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama didn't faint from exhaustion.
Comment: 1,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.93,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,I pulled two all-nighters making\NHayama-san's new maid outfit.
Comment: 1,0:15:45.06,0:15:50.23,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,I have my hands full with making a special\Nchocolate cake I'm giving to Youko-sama.
Comment: 1,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.73,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sonobe-san?
Comment: 1,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.08,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Oh, you're tired already, Hayama-san?
Comment: 1,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.72,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nishiyama-san.
Comment: 1,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.73,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Oh my, then would Kondou-san\Nlike to start working here, too?
Comment: 1,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.91,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll ask Sonobe-san next time.
Comment: 1,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.53,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama said that Sonobe-san likes\Nmaking people who dislike it wear them.
Comment: 1,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.98,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,That's why Nishiyama-san is a maid, too!
Comment: 1,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.78,Alt,sub 1,0,0,0,,Nishiyama-san... a maid?
Comment: 1,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.65,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama made these herself{from scratch}?
Comment: 1,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.04,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Youko-sama!
Comment: 1,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.87,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Oh, Tsuji-san!
Comment: 1,0:21:15.78,0:21:19.98,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Nishikawa-san... gave me chocolates!
Comment: 1,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.88,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Youko-sama?!
Comment: 1,0:23:43.13,0:23:45.78,Def_m,sub 1,0,0,0,,Let's have Youko-sama say the title.
