Comment: 1,0:23:43.13,0:23:47.08,sign_c,sub 1,0,0,0,,{\ybord57\xbord9\fs40\pos(997,142)}Let's have\NYouko-sama\Nsay the title.
Comment: 1,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.09,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Tsuji's ani.
Comment: 1,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.18,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Oh, you heard from your imouto.
Comment: 1,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.20,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for always\Ntaking care of my imouto.
Comment: 1,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.83,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,And I was even polite and said "thanks\Nfor always taking care of my imouto"!
Comment: 1,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.48,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,It's what a ani would do.
Comment: 1,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.46,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you idiot!
Comment: 1,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.76,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Wait— Onii-chan, you idiot!
Comment: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.88,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Comment: 1,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.38,Default,sub 1-3,0,0,0,,Onii-chan is popular at school after all.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankful to someone?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I am needed!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a present from me!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I lost...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You bind him with a scarf\Nembedded with wires...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.58,0:01:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally the season, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The season that I want winter to end soon\Nand hope I can save on my heating bill.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.53,0:01:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just have this conversation?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Valentine's!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's is an important day!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day to gorge on chocolate!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what Valentine's is for.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard this conversation before...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not planning to.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're thankful to someone,\Nyou can give some to them.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankful... to someone?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened the other day...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot get down from the tree.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really high up.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree looks thin, so it might\Nnot take my weight if I climb it.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I must rescue it!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I am needed!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more important things to do\Nthan make these useless things.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless things?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.18,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Yamaji helped me rescue the cat.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an event that's\Nmore fitting for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Event?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened to the cat?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.23,0:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after we got it down, it ran away.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over, just like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize I could not meet\Nyour expectations.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You set off a flag for it\Ncoming back to repay you.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Repay me?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.51,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard stories of animals\Nwho repay people for saving them.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this fish for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Salted salmon?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this cash for you, here!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cash?!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll let you touch\Nmy paw pads... just this once!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she gave it a personality, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.93,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yama—
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.43,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this might be a weird request.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.16,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If the kitten comes to repay you,\Nplease save the moment!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I understand.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bel?!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.69,0:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful that you\Ntook me in and were so kind to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a present from me!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That dream sounded like a farewell{Bel's last words}!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't a {\i1}bad{\i0} dream.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happened this morning.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She was repaying you.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the way a cat shows its love\Nis different from how humans show love.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.38,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to understand and receive that love\Nshows how good of an owner you are.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once an animal lover,\Nalways an animal lover.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a model pet owner.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something I can't ignore.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a very bold talk.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she has!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.03,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just having her by\Nmy side is a gift in itself.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how a pet owner should think?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes{Is it}?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you two have a competition\Nto see who cats like more?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you take pictures of your cat before?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever takes a cuter cat picture, wins!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still, Bel.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.58,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't come here!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.88,0:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My almost-tendinitis wrists that have been holding\Nthe camera since morning are quickly healing!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cute, I can't pick!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all best shots!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my pictures.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are my best shots.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will judge the results.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're cute.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They are very cute.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it is like comparing\Ntwo peas from the same pod.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she is cute.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so cute!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have this?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's trade.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get a real competition\Nbetween two cat fans, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.71,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the competition for, then?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we got something\Nout of it, so all is good.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we want a competition...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Odagiri Futaba!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a competitor.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.09,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably going\Nto challenge me, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} challenge you this time!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumbo hamburg!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let me in!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this one of the places\Nyou're banned from?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You had forgotten?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They let me in.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, I win by default!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Total victory for me!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I lost...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.98,0:09:43.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Oh yeah! Whoo!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, congratulations on your win.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, what was your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni... Ni... Nishi-something?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He only said the "Nishi" part, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nishikawa"!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ni-shi-ka-wa"!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Sasame told me.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're, uh, one of her friends, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well... er...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasame!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what, I won against Odagiri!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't win.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you said,\Nthat doesn't count as winning.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But she said "congratulations."
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was super being an adult.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.42,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, {that's}isn't what you {I'm }supposed to say to {your }friends?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if we were friends already.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.73,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Really}Oh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still building our friendship!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even say any—
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sasame!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any good ideas?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, memorable?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.20,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many types of chocolates\NI can eat with my allowance this year—
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.39,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think a hand-knitted scarf\Nand handmade chocolate is best?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, isn't that too normal?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.29,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You bind him with a scarf embedded with\Nwires and force-feed drugged chocolate.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.83,0:12:06.53,Alt,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get ready.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.28,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master Takezono\Nwill have a fine Valentine's.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.26,0:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to make chocolate.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.91,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, but my hearing\Nhas declined recently.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make chocolate!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to keep it as emergency food.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, for Valentine's!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And who will you be giving it to?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I will send a mountain\Nof chocolates to father, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to hike up\Na mountain with everyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am talking about Valentine's!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonobe.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make chocolate.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.03,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for the shop!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give homemade chocolate\Nto people I am thankful for.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will not slack\Non my duties here.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She will probably start off energetically,
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but get exhausted because\Nshe's not used to making sweets.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.13,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she'll be sick in bed, and Valentine's\Nwill be even busier than Christmas!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my situation.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you'll be helping me so much!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the person for the job.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to do\Non Valentine's anyway, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to pay me, either!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay me with cakes instead.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, too bad.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't have\Nto wear that maid dress.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All... right... mm, hmm...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's work hard today!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.84,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, they fit perfectly.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what we agreed on!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.59,0:14:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to wear {\i1}this{\i0} maid outfit,\Nso I prepared a different one for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.53,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.08,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make some for you two,\Ntoo, but I didn't have enough time.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is prepping for Valentine's that tough?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.38,0:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will allow people to enter\Nin order, so please do not push.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.63,0:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ring you up here once you have\Ndecided what items you would like.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why did she make {\i1}me{\i0} work, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how busy it is.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that other guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The former butler?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that now?!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She did say she hadn't slept for two nights.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she be sleeping when it's this busy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So easily manipulated...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the long wait.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} Valentine's.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's so busy!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Sonobe!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.03,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a short break, then.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.13,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes life hard for herself.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One limited edition Gâteau Chocolat.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one Gâteau Chocolat.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's the Tsuji siblings!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.56,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not a big deal if a guy\Nbuys Valentine's cakes.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.07,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.69,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of limited edition items\Nduring Valentine's and Christmas.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.01,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it take courage for a guy to buy\Nchocolate-flavored things around Valentine's?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.00,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.98,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I get tons of chocolate at school,\Nso it doesn't faze me.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that unexpected.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.38,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in my school club,\NI'm an important mascot character!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.23,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see Nishiyama\Nworking hard on the job.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing interesting to see here.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's awake?!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks, {\i1}that's{\i0} not my thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,If you agree now, I'll throw in a dessert.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}That's{\i0} not my thing"?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, no thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.24,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for working so hard.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to catch up on my sleep thanks to you!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was pretty tiring.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try on a maid outfit sometime, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't work.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.68,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She asked me to wear it,\Nand that was the only thing she had.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't wearing it because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want to wear those clothes again.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It fit you size-wise,\Nbut it didn't look that good.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like the clothes were wearing you.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.39,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You look better in more straight-cut clothes.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it looked pretty good on you...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually think that, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're complimenting\Nher when you usually don't.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your help yesterday.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.98,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is a thank you for everything,\Nincluding yesterday.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.23,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this the charcoal stuff\Nto get rid of odors?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're truffles!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them myself{from scratch}.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the gratitude I have for you\Ninto them when I made them.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't melt, but they're edible.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it if I try.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not melting?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.98,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.23,0:21:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolates?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please accept them.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,More?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a house or something?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I get some... too?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will offer them on the family altar!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just eat them.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.88,0:21:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolates should arrive\Nto father today, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all of them.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.98,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the chocolates of gratitude for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Sonobe Shino.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Nishikawa Family's former maid.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is so entertaining.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
