Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.54,Alt,all,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.46,0:02:41.11,Default,all,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.09,Default,all,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.73,Default,all,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.28,Default,all,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.54,Default,all,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.99,Default,fix,0,0,0,,My, if the kitten came to repay me,\Nit would be so cute and{. That would be } lovely indeed.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.23,Default,fix,0,0,0,,So cheap!{That's it?}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.79,0:04:19.68,Default,fix,0,0,0,,You called?{I'm at your service.}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.39,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.25,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Oh my!{Wow.}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.43,Default,fix,0,0,0,,I guess, maybe it's a tie.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.38,Default,fix,0,0,0,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.96,Default,fix,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let me in,\Nbecause I'm a bigger threat!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.53,Default,fix,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.03,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.83,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Think about it seriously!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.38,Default,fix,0,0,0,,It's my... pleasure...?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.33,Default,fix,0,0,0,,This time of year is as busy as\NChristmas, so even a cat's paw—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.93,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Why not {You can just }ask someone else?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.63,Default,fix,0,0,0,,I refuse{No, thank you}.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.63,0:14:17.35,Default,fix,0,0,0,,I will properly pay you for your work.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.58,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Wait a second{Hey}!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.58,Default,fix,0,0,0,,What's the deal with these clothes{Why am I wearing these clothes}?!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.43,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Now, now.{It's fine.}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.61,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, you're a capable woman after all{You take care of things when it counts!}.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.57,Default,fix,0,0,0,,O-Of course{Y-You bet}!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.77,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, right away{. How can I help you}.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.23,Default,fix,0,0,0,,As expected from a capable woman{ someone who can take care of things when it counts}, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.01,Default,fix,0,0,0,,He saves up a lot of money for this!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.78,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Ah, it makes sense now.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.78,0:19:30.53,Default,fix,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.38,Default,fix,0,0,0,,I don't like wearing it or anything!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.78,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, right, that's right.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.10,Default,fix,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure{F-For me}?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.48,0:21:23.03,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What {should I give back to her}to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.38,Default,fix,0,0,0,,What to do{How much should my return} about gift's cost?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.98,0:21:28.43,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Two times? Three times more?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.55,Default,fix,0,0,0,,Here, for you too, Yamaji.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.09,0:02:18.65,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko, do you plan\Nto give chocolate to anyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.83,0:04:16.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Where's Yamaji?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.56,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.62,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.09,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.90,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru, thanks for always taking care of me!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.38,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,It's because of Miss Youko's story.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.97,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Good for you, Hayama.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.37,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama's a model pet owner?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.83,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Then, Nishiyama, this happen\Nto you too, I wonder?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.18,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Eru giving you a repayment gift I mean.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.18,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Master Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,And it's {\i1}Miss{\i0} Nishikawa Youko to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.76,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Add the "Miss" you glutton!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.31,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko is being considerate!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.48,0:10:56.81,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You know, uh, Nishi... hara... kawa... tani...?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.03,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,It's Nishikawa.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Right, right, Nishikawa!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.03,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Why did you say weird things to Nishikawa?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.83,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You probably made Nishikawa feel awkward!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.73,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Nishikawa and I aren't that close yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.89,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,When I give Yuu the chocolates,\NI want it to be memorable.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.48,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,So that's what Miss Usuda is planning?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.73,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,—or rather Miss Youko's paw,\Nwould be helpful.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.18,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko wants to make\Nhandmade chocolate{ from scratch}?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.98,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,I was asking Nishiyama to\Ngive me a hand at the shop.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.21,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,By all means{I would love if you could help out}, Hayama too.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.01,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko didn't faint from exhaustion.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,I pulled two all-nighters making\NHayama's new maid outfit.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.06,0:15:50.23,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,I have my hands full with making a special\Nchocolate cake I'm giving to Miss Youko.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.73,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Miss Sonobe?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.08,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Oh, you're tired already, Hayama?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.72,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.73,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Oh my, then would you like\Nto start working here, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.91,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll ask Miss Sonobe next time.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.53,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko said that Miss Sonobe likes\Nmaking people who dislike it wear them.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.98,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,That's why Nishiyama is a maid, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.78,Alt,sub 2,0,0,0,,Nishiyama... a maid?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.65,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko made these herself{from scratch}?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.04,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Miss Youko!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.87,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Oh, Tsuji!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.78,0:21:19.98,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Nishikawa... gave me chocolates!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.88,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Youko?!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.13,0:23:45.78,Def_m,sub 2,0,0,0,,Let's have Miss Youko say the title.
