Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.13,0:23:47.08,sign_c,sub 2,0,0,0,,{\ybord57\xbord9\fs40\pos(997,142)}Let's have\NMiss Youko\Nsay the title.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.09,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,The older Tsuji sibling.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.18,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Oh, you heard from your sister.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.20,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for always\Ntaking care of my sister.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.83,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,And I was even polite and said "thanks\Nfor always taking care of my sister"!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.48,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,It's what a big bro would do.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.46,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Brother, you idiot!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.76,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Wait— brother, you idiot!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.88,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Big sister!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.38,Default,sub 1-2,0,0,0,,Brother is popular at school after all.
